The default `RubrixLogHTTPMiddleware` [record mapper for token classification](https://github.com/recognai/rubrix/blob/master/src/rubrix/client/asgi.py#L35) expect a structured including a `text` field for inputs. This could make prediction model inputs a bit cumbersome. Default mapper could accepts also flat strings as inputs:

```python
def token_classification_mapper(inputs, outputs):
    if isinstance(inputs, str):
        text = inputs
